Package it.unibo.csr.big.cubeload.generator

Class Profile

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unibo.csr.big.cubeload.generator.Profile
  • public class Profile
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implements the concept of profile. The profile's features describe its characterization: seed queries, session length range etc. In this class the full list of sessions is formed and returned.
